Business Brief -- Image Entertainment Inc.:
   Mitsubishi to Buy Stock,
   Signs Manufacturing Accord
Image also entered into a nonexclusive laser disk
manufacturing agreement with Mitsubishi Corp. under which
Mitsubishi will become a significant manufacturing source for
the company. Terms of the agreement weren't disclosed.
   In December, Image signed a four-year laser disk licensing
pact with Walt Disney Co., and granted Disney a warrant to
buy 1,670,000 of its 10.9 million common shares outstanding
at $6 each.
   In over-the-counter trading yesterday Image shares fell 50
cents to $11.50.